      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 14,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 14:3",
      "text": "ܐܝܢܐ ܕܝܢ ܕܡܬܢܒܐ ܠܒܢܝܢܫܐ ܡܡܠܠ ܒܢܝܢܐ ܘܠܘܒܒܐ ܘܒܘܝܐܐ ܀",
