      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 14,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 14:4",
      "text": "ܕܡܡܠܠ ܒܠܫܢܐ ܢܦܫܗ ܗܘ ܒܢܐ ܘܕܡܬܢܒܐ ܥܕܬܐ ܒܢܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
